<li><strong>IEEE International Conference on Acoustic, Speech, and Signal Processing (ICASSP) 2018:</strong> Co-organizer of the special session on Cybersecurity and Privacy.</li>
<li><strong>IEEE International Conference on Computing, Networking and Communications (IEEE ICNC) 2018:</strong> Chair of the Cognitive Computing and Networking symposium.</li>
<li><strong>Asilomar Conference on Signals, Systems, and Computers 2017:</strong> Organizer of the invited Cognitive Networks session. </li>
<li><strong>IEEE International Conference on Sensing, Communication and Networking (IEEE SECON) 2017</strong>: TPC Vice Chair for Submissions.</li>
